kb3.name: kb3_systems
kb3.structure: CREATE TABLE `kb3_systems` ( `sys_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `sys_con_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `sys_name` char(128) NOT NULL, `sys_x` float NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `sys_y` float NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `sys_z` float NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `sys_sec` decimal(12,5) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00000', PRIMARY KEY (`sys_id`), KEY `sys_con_id` (`sys_con_id`), KEY `sys_name` (`sys_name`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=31002605 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8
